{
  "stem": "15577.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are very busy, because, first of all, because it was a Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we learned both-- Polish and secular and Hebrew subjects.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were four Hebrew subjects, which were-- were additional to the normal subjects, which the Poles-- because we're obliged to learn.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By the way, the matriculation, the end of the school, we needed to make two-- two kind of exams, one in Polish and one in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So our school lasted longer than normal Polish schools.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we came home later than Polish kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we had much more homework to do than the Polish kids, again, because of the two languages we have been taught.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we met with the-- we have been most of us hand some some learning about the language, or music, or something like this It was a-- it was additional occupation.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then we met, and played, and met-- had friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Vacations, we went mostly with the family, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not far from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And mostly, we stayed-- if you speak about vacations during the summer, you-- the vacations were two months.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we stayed mostly, the whole two months, in someplace, which-- at least with my mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Fathers were mostly coming at weekends to join the families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as I told you, we have been in rather good conditions, so mostly the nanny or somebody was coming with us, to help the mother, as long as we were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had a-- a big fabric store, which was partially wholesale and partially retail.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, speaking about the conditions from before the war in Cracow, it was rather a big business.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
